==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Toon
<hw>Toon</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind. <ets>tun</ets>,
<ets>t⟦umac⟧n</ets>, Skr. <ets>tunna</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The reddish brown wood of an East Indian tree (<spn>Cedrela
Toona</spn>) closely resembling the Spanish cedar; also. the tree
itself.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

